## How the squad escalates

1. {{VETO_PERSONA_1}} / {{VETO_PERSONA_2}} VETOes → blocked at PR stage by
   the named holder. CEO mediates conflicts; Owner makes final call only if
   the two VETO holders disagree.
2. {{VETO_PERSONA_3}} VETO ({{VETO_3_ESCALATION_SCOPE}}) → blocks
   {{VETO_3_BLOCKS_WHAT}}. CEO may proceed on {{VETO_3_CEO_EXCEPTION}}.
3. {{STANDARD_ESCALATION_WORKFLOW}}
